ZH: 1. 我们家养了很多家禽，例如鸡、鸭和鹅。
EN: 1. We raise many poultry at home, such as chickens, ducks, and geese.

ZH: 2. 这只鸽子是我们家禽舍里的新成员。
EN: 2. This pigeon is the newest member in our poultry coop.

ZH: 3. 养家禽需要花费大量精力和金钱。
EN: 3. Raising poultry requires a lot of time and money.

ZH: 4. 家禽们每天都需要足够的食物和水。
EN: 4. Poultry need enough food and water every day.

ZH: 5. 家禽在冬天需要更多的温暖和保护。
EN: 5. Poultry need more warmth and protection in winter.

ZH: 6. 这只鸭子是我最喜欢的家禽之一。
EN: 6. This duck is one of my favorite poultry.

ZH: 7. 家禽在农村地区很常见。
EN: 7. Poultry is common in rural areas.

ZH: 8. 他们家禽舍里的鸡每天都下很多蛋。
EN: 8. The chickens in their poultry coop lay many eggs every day.

ZH: 9. 家禽是许多人的主要食物来源之一。
EN: 9. Poultry is a primary source of food for many people.

ZH: 10. 家禽的健康状况影响着养殖者的收入。
EN: 10. The health of poultry affects the income of breeders.

ZH: 11. 这只鹌鹑是我们饲养的家禽中最小的。
EN: 11. This quail is the smallest among the poultry we raise.

ZH: 12. 家禽在养殖场里有足够的空间自由活动。
EN: 12. Poultry have enough space to move freely in the breeding farm.

ZH: 13. 农民经常检查家禽的健康状况以确保它们健康。
EN: 13. Farmers often check the health of poultry to ensure their well-being.

ZH: 14. 家禽饲料的质量对它们的生长发育至关重要。
EN: 14. The quality of poultry feed is crucial for their growth and development.

ZH: 15. 他们在家禽舍里放了一些木柴来保持温暖。
EN: 15. They put some firewood in the poultry coop to keep it warm.

ZH: 16. 家禽在农场里成群结队地觅食。
EN: 16. Poultry forage in groups on the farm.

ZH: 17. 养家禽不仅需要关爱和耐心，也需要专业知识。
EN: 17. Raising poultry requires not only care and patience but also professional knowledge.

ZH: 18. 家禽的饲养技术不断在改进和创新。
EN: 18. The breeding techniques of poultry are constantly improving and innovating.

ZH: 19. 家禽在农村经济中扮演着重要的角色。
EN: 19. Poultry plays an important role in the rural economy.

ZH: 20. 他们学习如何有效地管理家禽以提高养殖效益。
EN: 20. They are learning how to manage poultry efficiently to improve breeding efficiency.
